Overview

This repository presents the development and validation of an Integrated Vehicle Health Management (IVHM) framework for aerospace platforms using NI VeriStand, LabVIEW, and National Instruments hardware.

The project focuses on real-time monitoring, fault detection, diagnostics, automated testing, and Hardware-in-the-Loop validation of aerospace systems.

Objectives

Design an IVHM architecture
Acquire real-time sensor data
Interface NI DAQ hardware
Develop automated health monitoring algorithms
Perform Hardware-in-the-Loop testing
Inject faults for validation
Verify subsystem performance
Generate diagnostic reports

